---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Υπηρεσίες - Updated Layout" active="services">

<main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<!-- Header Section -->
<header class="mb-20 text-center md:text-left">
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4 block font-body">ΕΞΕΙΔΙΚΕΥΜΕΝΗ ΦΡΟΝΤΙΔΑ</span>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold font-headline leading-tight tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-6">
                Οι Υπηρεσίες Μας
            </h1>
<p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-body">
                Προσεγγίζουμε τη διατροφή ως ένα μέσο ίασης και ευεξίας, προσφέροντας εξατομικευμένα προγράμματα που σέβονται τις ανάγκες του σώματός σας.
            </p>
</header>
<!-- Bento Grid Services -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
<!-- Service Card 1: Clinical Nutrition (Large Focus) -->
<div class="md:col-span-8 group bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative border border-outline-variant/10">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full">
<div class="md:w-1/2 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between">
<div>
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container" data-icon="medical_services">medical_services</span>
</div>
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Κλινική Διατροφή</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 font-body">
                                Διαχείριση παθολογικών καταστάσεων μέσω στοχευμένης διατροφής. Αντιμετώπιση διαβήτη, καρδιαγγειακών νοσημάτων και γαστρεντερικών διαταραχών με επιστημονική τεκμηρίωση.
                            </p>
</div>
<a href="/services/clinical-nutrition" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold group-hover:gap-4 transition-all font-body">
                            Μάθετε Περισσότερα 
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="md:w-1/2 h-64 md:h-auto overflow-hidden">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" data-alt="close-up of fresh organic vegetables and medical stethoscope on a light wooden table reflecting a clinical yet natural healthcare setting" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCf9bi8sdX63K-7eQwj5bniNGr_7m0sgkDZuuz8zjGlBPMK4nahSKzTKQQGbT0cUdgxl-o9AjqjUuApDdMJZpegFyHcbkY2bJpc5P5fdjkCZfXhIz34BDH-a8l5ucWvyrrWMUcX9wlFH19tvSoV0ffsFL-xiH0TFh0zXjVmT3mjyhUJWDZMA2DiLwz0vW6_MeC_KLxp3u2frgezfJHmwaOx_9D_EbWfdk9fD7BhpHgWcZtuEU10reJkH3TBEvGBVddDYX24776oWYA"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Service Card 2: Weight Loss -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 group bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-1 shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] flex flex-col">
<div class="h-64 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" data-alt="colorful healthy salad bowl with avocado and seeds on a bright sunny morning kitchen background with soft bokeh" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDJ53WrHUylKReVhwlLHL5zHJUQlOMQXNqCKJunL45Eol4zbyYNAwxSm3_ViWRWk1eCV49zNdWt8nJEs9E_gp_aZd-yMF7ItAnrYRZGlwdfC48FO8oyB2CJRO5h1wQGmCs9x41pNyxSNtgFwTcpMpkbt0yPd8FtzAbt8RRHKrrRlM05ctCfs9V2IkT1fUr8KOivBCgW1QV5smYDiRysShpeQjLbe01DKhIoubnVNj6tCQMstV2smkAAPT-WoitbJzRjQWTYEvehsuA"/>
</div>
<div class="px-6 pb-8 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-between">
<div>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-3">Απώλεια Βάρους</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 font-body">
                            Μόνιμα αποτελέσματα χωρίς στερητικές δίαιτες. Εστιάζουμε στην επανεκπαίδευση της γεύσης και στη δημιουργία υγιών συνηθειών.
                        </p>
</div>
<a href="/services/weight-management" class="w-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-all font-body text-center block">
                        Μάθετε Περισσότερα
                    </a>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Service Card 3: Sports Nutrition -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 group bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-1 shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] flex flex-col">
<div class="h-64 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" data-alt="close-up of athlete hands preparing a protein shake with nuts and oats in a modern bright fitness studio" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuACRlBU8RahZ3mG-YVBbpxMt2JIqiyPt0mT55yOxF4-WNfWWaIWbJ4mHJ8PjZDUhC4H9a2Uknw4kuE5vckdimTXtFBhJg9ofNPFzLrfeBFIRRqMeJE8itT1bSielA0vVnw2SXUNaE25DLM4GIEKfE9QYPiVV0pMm0SXJxyOwRAl9jZuxfoZeR7rDyVIA3ZKruJniANpCa6cSTgAPmkPHG0GeM5AHD5BU9iUq0n1Cs_0n7rNHE_zkr8Ydny9CZjNNEJfw-YIyJFDZPg"/>
</div>
<div class="px-6 pb-8 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-between">
<div>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-3">Αθλητική Διατροφή</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 font-body">
                            Βελτιστοποίηση της απόδοσης και της αποκατάστασης. Εξειδικευμένα πλάνα για ερασιτέχνες και επαγγελματίες αθλητές.
                        </p>
</div>
<a href="/services/sports-nutrition" class="w-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-all font-body text-center block">
                        Μάθετε Περισσότερα
                    </a>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Service Card 4: Additional (Nutrition Education) -->
<div class="md:col-span-8 group bg-primary-container rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full">
<div class="md:w-1/2 h-64 md:h-auto overflow-hidden order-last md:order-first">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 mix-blend-overlay grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" data-alt="group of people attending an intimate wellness workshop with organic snacks and journals in a bright airy studio" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCq06Qs4E8tpsRxWl7g8Z96ASt96ogp4JXXLoIIdg_ARTmEY3vKdZpurIDrgIqv0uboPYuNZJb9bAnYB6TqwV90V8FhWUa9dJj1-o3Fn7fkPNLQPsrPwkeaRIeXgRQ7gonw9uRiVlmzQI-5qaZPxyXJaSa0w60JgG4uP2h2HOzH9IU0sisFHPCVEqlGVCauXuk9nM6JhDo0ysY8nlQjfPktaC1UxXQFBUn0dkhzHqRWwLhBgTPG2_ULD0VxyF3sY9IYomYttrZfCoA"/>
</div>
<div class="md:w-1/2 p-10 flex flex-col justify-center bg-primary text-on-primary">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Διατροφική Εκπαίδευση</h2>
<p class="text-primary-fixed/80 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-body">
                            Σεμινάρια και εργαστήρια για να μάθετε να επιλέγετε τις σωστές πρώτες ύλες και να μαγειρεύετε υγιεινά και νόστιμα για εσάς και την οικογένειά σας.
                        </p>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<span class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-primary-fixed/30 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider font-body">Workshops</span>
<span class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-primary-fixed/30 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider font-body">E-Learning</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Tonal Layering Section -->
<section class="mt-24 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden py-20 px-10 md:px-16">
<div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<!-- Left Side: Text Content -->
<div class="text-left">
<h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-headline mb-8 leading-tight">Δεν είστε σίγουροι από πού να ξεκινήσετε;</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-lg font-body">
                        Κλείστε μια δωρεάν 15λεπτη συμβουλευτική συνεδρία για να συζητήσουμε τους στόχους σας και να βρούμε την υπηρεσία που σας ταιριάζει.
                    </p>
</div>
<!-- Right Side: Contact Form -->
<div class="w-full">
<form method="POST" action="#" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/20 w-full">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="block text-sm font-bold text-on-surface-variant ml-1 font-body" for="name">Ονοματεπώνυμο</label>
<input name="name" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border-none bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface placeholder:text-on-surface-variant/50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all font-body" id="name" placeholder="Πώς σας λένε;" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="block text-sm font-bold text-on-surface-variant ml-1 font-body" for="email">Email</label>
<input name="email" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border-none bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface placeholder:text-on-surface-variant/50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all font-body" id="email" placeholder="email@example.com" type="email"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
<label class="block text-sm font-bold text-on-surface-variant ml-1 font-body" for="subject">Θέμα</label>
<div class="relative">
<select name="subject" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border-none bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface appearance-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all font-body" id="subject">
<option>Γενική Ερώτηση</option>
<option>Κλινική Διατροφή</option>
<option>Απώλεια Βάρους</option>
<option>Αθλητική Διατροφή</option>
<option>Διατροφική Εκπαίδευση</option>
</select>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none text-on-surface-variant">expand_more</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2 mb-8">
<label class="block text-sm font-bold text-on-surface-variant ml-1 font-body" for="message">Μήνυμα</label>
<textarea name="message" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border-none bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface placeholder:text-on-surface-variant/50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all resize-none font-body" id="message" placeholder="Περιγράψτε τι σας απασχολεί..." rows="4"></textarea>
</div>
<button class="w-full md:w-auto bg-primary text-on-primary px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-body" type="submit">
                            Αποστολή
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">send</span>
</button>
</form>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Decorative Grain/Texture Gradient Placeholder -->
<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-primary-container via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
</section>
</main>
</Layout>
